<HEADLINE> UAE to Hold Internet Exhibition </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ABU DHABI, January 18 (Xinhua) -- An Internet exhibition
conference is to be held here next month, said Ahmed Alhosani, an
official from the Emirates Telecommunications Corporation, on
Monday.
</P>
<P>
The Internet World Middle East '99 (IWME), to be held from
February 22 to 24, will feature "live" demonstrations of how
businesses can use the Internet to reduce operating costs and
boost bottom lines.
</P>
<P>
