past year," said John Hassett, general manager of the Trade Fairs
and Conferences Ltd., which is one of the sponsors of the event.
</P>
<P>
Also the exhibition will be highlighted by an awards ceremony
for the best usage of e-commerce, the most creative website, best
information website and best Arabic website, said a press release
issued by the organizers.
</P>
<P>
High profile industry experts from six nations, including
Egypt, Jordan, Saudi Arabia, the United Arab Emirates, Britain and
the U.S. will address the conference.
</P>
