infrastructural facilities such as highways, railways, bridges
and docks.
</P>
<P>
Other key areas open to overseas investors include
agriculture, public utilities, high-tech industries and upgrading
state-owned enterprises, according to Wang.
</P>
<P>
The province will also experiment with overseas investments in
the retail, tourism, foreign trade, construction and
transportation sectors.
</P>
<P>
Shandong has approved more than 20,000 overseas-funded
projects in recent year, with total contracted investments of
32.3 billion US dollars.  
