gold, copper and iron ore in Latin America, and fishing in Latin
America and Africa, Wang said.
</P>
<P>
Key manufacturers of textiles, building materials, electronics
and other products have been encouraged to establish production
and assembly lines in foreign countries.
</P>
<P>
This year, some 100 state-owned and township enterprise groups
and 20 large private businesses are expected to go abroad seeking
opportunities and hoping to establish at least 20 projects.
