<HEADLINE> South China to Open New International Airport </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HAIKOU, January 18 (Xinhua) --Hainan's Meilan International
Airport will soon be open after being given the green light by
aviation experts.
</P>
<P>
The airport covers an area of 569 hectares and has a 3,600
meters runway.
</P>
<P>
Construction on this key project began three years ago and it
has cost 2.3 billion yuan, with most of it's major equipment
imported from abroad. 
</P>
